        "text_1_heading": "Thank You for Being Part of Our Community",
        "text_1_body": "<p>At Yumbud, we believe care should extend beyond the dogs we serve at home.<br/><br/>Founded in Los Angeles, Yumbud was created with a simple intention: to make thoughtful, wholesome treats for dogs while contributing to a kinder pet community. Every recipe we create is guided by love, quality, and respect for the special bond between people and their pets.<br/><br/>When you choose Yumbud, you are not only giving your dog a treat made with care — you are helping us support animals who are still waiting for safety, comfort, and a loving home.<br/><br/>Yumbud is committed to giving back to local animal welfare organizations in Los Angeles and surrounding communities.<br/><br/>Our give-back efforts focus on supporting trusted organizations such as:<br/><br/>LA Animal Services<br/>Supporting shelter animals and community programs that help keep pets and families together.<br/><br/>Pasadena Humane<br/>Supporting animal care, pet food assistance, and resources for pets and pet families in need.<br/><br/>Best Friends Animal Society Los Angeles<br/>Supporting lifesaving programs for homeless pets and efforts to create a more compassionate future for animals.<br/><br/>Through product donations, community support, and a portion of selected proceeds, we hope to help bring comfort, nourishment, and care to pets who need it most.</p>",
